overview: Responding to the flyers they have picked up on campus, seven star-struck babes turn up to audition for a major talent show. They do their solo acts, but then the 'judges' tell them that they are really only interested in their sexual skills. So each girl gets naked, sucks cock and fucks for fame. Starring Jennifer Anderson, Giselle Capri, Syndi Fox, Kirra Lynne, Dominique Perez, Nikki Vee & Missy Vega.
title: T&A Tryouts
